high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the counter.
Pick up the butter knife off of the counter.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk towards the wall, turn right to face the sink.
Put the butter knife in the sink and turn on the sink, after a couple seconds turn the sink off and take out the now clean butter knife.
Walk over to the wooden table behind you.
Put the clean butter knife on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean butter knife on a wooden table.

high_descs: turn to the right to face the counter with the tomato sitting on it
move to the counter and pick up the butter knife that is behind the tomato
move to the left slightly to face the sink
pick the knife in to the sink, turn on the water to clean the knife, turn off the water and remove the knife from the sink
turn around and move across the room to the end of the long brown table on the right, turn right to face the table in front of the loaf of bread
put the knife on the table to the right of the loaf of bread
anns.task_desc: put a clean butter knife on to the table

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk to the counter with the tomato on it.
Pick up the knife that is behind the tomato.
Move to your left to the sink.
Place the knife in the sink and turn on the faucet to partially fill the sink with water, wash the knife, drain the sink, pick the knife up.
Turn and walk in the direction of the door, hang a right to the table to the right of the door.
Place the knife to the right of the loaf of bread on the left end of the table.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a knife, wash the knife, place it on the table
